              "content": "=Analyze this wallet data for its \"Personality\":\n\n{{ $json.geminiInput }}\n\nInstructions:\n\nIdentify if this is a \"Patient Investor\", \"Degen/Gambler\", or \"Bot/Airdrop Hunter\".\n\nGive a 2-line creative summary in Hinglish/Urdu.\n\nGive a Risk Score (1-10)."
